  "description": "Mono legato bass with portamento — sawtooth folded for grit, slow bounce gravity, filter envelope punching through at hard velocity. Glide at 0.08 seconds. LFO1 at 0.2 Hz gives the bassline a subtle spectral pulse. Prism minimal, phaser dry. The foundation stone for RTJ-style bass work.",
